des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your SIMON AIRE products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "SIMON AIRE" app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our "SIMON AIRE" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search "SIMON-AIRE" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable "SIMON-AIRE" skill, and you'll be navigated to "SIMON-AIRE" login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on thermostat.
Alexa, turn off thermostat.
Alexa, set thermostat to heat.
Alexa, set thermostat to 20 degrees.
Alexa, turn on air conditioner.
Alexa, make it warmer in here.
